---
title: Beef and Mushroom Curry with rice and yoghurt drizzle
description: This Indian-inspired curry features beef mince, mushrooms and plenty of flavour. A blend of North Indian Spices and rogan josh paste makes for the perfect balance between heat and seasoning in this satisfying and delicious meal.
